^ Howard BV, Manson JE, Stefanick ML; 等. Low-fat dietary pattern and weight change over 7 years: the Women's Health Initiative Dietary Modification Trial. JAMA: the Journal of the American Medical Association. 2006, 295 (1): 39–49. PMID 16391215. doi:10.1001/jama.295.1.39.  引文格式1維護：顯式使用等標籤 (link)
^ Howard BV, Van Horn L, Hsia J; 等. Low-fat dietary pattern and risk of cardiovascular disease: the Women's Health Initiative Randomized Controlled Dietary Modification Trial. JAMA : the Journal of the American Medical Association. 2006, 295 (6): 655–66. PMID 16467234. doi:10.1001/jama.295.6.655.  引文格式1維護：顯式使用等標籤 (link)
^ Fats and Cholesterol: Out with the Bad, In with the Good — What Should You Eat? – The Nutrition Source — Harvard School of Public Health. [2009-05-12]. 


