 科學

 化學


 看另一則問題 










            關於脂質分析的化學問題
        


請問digitonide derivative是怎樣的一個實驗呢?我知道它是用來實驗沉澱膽固醇,但詳細情形不是很清楚,網路上也查了很久,希望有高手可以替我解答這個問題^^





 
追蹤 


 
 1 個解答 
1


檢舉不當使用









您確定要刪除此解答嗎？
是
否












 









抱歉，似乎發生一些問題。



Trending Now





 

解答














最佳解答: 
             Digitonin Precipitation. For precipitation of 3-beta-hydroxy sterols, a solution of 1 % digitonin in 60% (v/v) ethanol was added to a solution of sterols in 60% ethanol at 60 C. After standing overnight, the resulting digitonide was separated  by low speed centrifugation and decantation of the liquid.The precipitate was washed several times with ethanol and then with anhydrous diethyl ether. The resulting white pellet digitonide, freed of most of the pigments, was dried.具3-beta-OH基的固醇(如膽固醇)可與digitonin 形成低溶解性的複合物 因而沈澱出來實驗方法:在60oC 下 1 % 的digitonin (溶於 60% ethanol水溶液(v/v) )  加進含有固醇樣品中(也是於 60% ethanol水溶液) 加完後於室溫靜置過夜 沈澱物(digitonide derivative)離心 沈澱物以乙醇 乙醚洗幾次 晾乾Plant Physiol. (1974) 53, 244-249ISSIDORIDES, C. H., I. KITAGAWA, AND E. 'MOSETTIG. 1962. Cleavage of steroidal(ligitonides in dimethyl sulfoxide. J. Org. Chem. 27: 4693-4694.PATTERSON, G. W. 1971. Relation between structure and retention time ofsterols in gas chromatography. Anal. Chem. 43: 1165-1170.http://www.clinchem.org/cgi/content/abstract/19/6/608 




 參考資料： 
 


